# File Permissions in Linux

This folder contains Linux file and directory permission commands used in administration and DevOps tasks.

## Common Commands

ls -l                    # View permissions
chmod 755 file.sh        # Change permission
chmod +x script.sh       # Make file executable
chmod -w file.txt        # Remove write permission

chown user file.txt      # Change file owner
chown user:group file.txt # Change owner and group

umask                    # Show default permissions
umask 022                # Set default permissions
